# Graph DSA Roadmap

1. Graph Representation
2. BFS
3. DFS
4. Connected Components
5. Number of Islands
6. Cycle Detection
7. Bipartite Graph
8. Topological Sort
9. Shortest Path (BFS)
10. Dijkstra
11. Bellman Ford
12. Floyd Warshall
13. MST (Prim + Kruskal)
14. Disjoint Set
15. SCC (Kosaraju/Tarjan)
16. Bridges & Articulation Points

Master BFS, DFS, Cycle Detection, Bipartite Graph, Topological Sort, Dijkstra, and Disjoint Set first—these form the foundation for most graph interview questions.
